      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Boundary conditions applied in the CFD model must be demonstrated equivalent to measured experimental inlet/outlet conditions; any discrepancies must be propagated as uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles in the CFD model are derived from idealised plug-flow assumptions rather than measured PIV profiles. The equivalency between assumed and actual boundary conditions has not been quantified. Not assessed."
