    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted as a complete submission for regulatory review purposes. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or formally flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels, confirming the decision outcome of Not Accepted for the underlying model claim. Six factors remain not-assessed and are documented as gaps. The package is accepted as a faithful record of the current credibility state; the model itself is not accepted for COU2 regulatory use until all required credibility levels are achieved.",
